**Alder's status:** ❤️❤️❤️ &nbsp; 🪄 2 charges &nbsp; 🗡️ Dagger +1 *(looted from vault guard)* &nbsp; 📜 Scroll of Light &nbsp; 🍄 Spore pouch

> *Bioluminescent caps cast everything in cold blue-green. The myconids communicate by puffing spores — right now they're saying something that sounds like your name.*

**Pro tip:** Cast *Scroll of Light* near a spore vent to ignite the gas. Clears a room but costs 1 ❤️.

